r relevante, krebsspezifische Nebenwirkungen verhindert, sondern auch die medizinische Therapiedosierung erhalten und Krankenhaustage reduziert werden können.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aCancerxDiagnosis. 0aCancerxTreatment. 0aMedical rehabilitation. 4aBewegungstherapie. 4aKrebs. 4aOnkologie. 4aPrähabilitation. 4aTumoren. 7aMEDICAL / Sports Medicine.2bisacsh  aMovement therapy.  acancer.  aoncology.  aprehabilitation.  atumors.1 aBaumann, Freerk T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBaumann, Freerk, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHallek, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKoll, Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeudecker, Julia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeudecker, Julia.1 aOverbeek, Remco, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOverbeek, Remco.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2019z9783110606386oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831105220510 cprintz978311052189440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311052241940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110522419423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110522419.jpg  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DPMb2019